ras/b6ce1ad39ee3793310510330fecbb5ff.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>96 Handcrafted Levels</strong> <br>Each puzzle is carefully designed to tickle your brain while keeping things chill and relaxing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌎 <strong>8 Unique Chapters</strong> <br>Explore different cozy environments—<strong>Home, City, Farm, Forest, and Exotic</strong>—each with its own set of adorable creatures and charming backgrounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦉 <strong>30 Big-Eyed, Quirky Animals</strong><br>Collect a variety of <strong>funny, expressive creatures</strong>, from a snooty borzoi to a sneaky rat, each with a personality of its own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👀 <strong>Hilarious, Interactive Eyes</strong><br>Animals’ <strong>eyes follow your cursor</strong>, creating funny, goofy expressions. And when you solve a puzzle—<strong>watch their eyes sparkle with pure joy!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/dbab60e4684e064459b5f30d90051b5c.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>Animals Collection</strong><br>Unlock and collect <strong>every fluffy friend</strong>, then admire them in your animals collection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Multiple Solutions for Every Puzzle</strong><br>Think outside the box! Each puzzle has <strong>several valid solutions</strong>, giving you space to experiment and play your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>A Hint System That Helps—Without Spoiling the Fun</strong><br>Stuck? No worries! Our hint system gives <strong>gentle nudges</strong> while letting you keep the fun of discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.webm?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/90197925b2a77bd4abc065e2859142da.mp4?t=1771093721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖌 <strong>Charming Hand-Drawn Art & Animations</strong><br>Each animal is <strong>lovingly illustrated and animated</strong> to bring out its personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 <strong>Relaxing Music & Cozy Sound Design</strong><br>Enjoy a <strong>soothing jazz soundtrack</strong> that makes puzzle-solving a relaxing escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📔 <strong>A Crafty Notebook Interface</strong><br>The game’s UI <strong>feels like a cozy scrapbook</strong>, adding to its warm and inviting atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😆 <strong>Funny & Playful Vibes</strong><br>Mess with the animals’ eyes, find all the creatures, enjoy the music, and just <strong>have fun!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156370/extras/99d08735c5a20d053349e9a0539558f5.poster.avif?t=1771093721\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass